Optimization is trying to find the way to run a company in a way that it can be most efficient and produce the largest profit. Example would be if you are selling books and magazines. Optimization is to maximize profits by determining how many of each books and magazines you need to sell to maximize profits. 
Linear programming model as components like desicion variables which are the variables that you are trying to find out. Objective function is the main problem or question you are trying to figure out. changing variables are the variables that you change in order to answer your objective function.
